OL,3,CChocolate makers create UK's 'biggest
OL,4,Cand heaviest' Easter egg
OL,6,FAn independent British chocolate brand
OL,7,Fhas created an Easter egg which it
OL,8,Fclaims is the UK's biggest and
OL,9,Fheaviest.
OL,11,FKent-based Cocoba made the chocolate
OL,12,Fcreation, which weighs nearly 300kg
OL,13,Fand stands at 7ft tall, over about
OL,14,Ffive days after many hours of planning.
OL,16,FIt has been given the name 'The Good
OL,17,FEgg' because once Easter has passed,
OL,18,Fit will be melted down and turned into
OL,19,Fabout 3,000 limited edition chocolate
OL,20,Fbars, with a percentage of profits
OL,21,Fsupporting local charities.
