OL,3,CChocolate makers create UK's 'biggest
OL,4,Cand heaviest' Easter egg
OL,6,FPiecing together the mammoth
OL,7,Fhandiwork, which is equivalent in
OL,8,Fweight to three baby elephants, was
OL,9,Fnot an easy feat, taking two attempts
OL,10,Fto get right.
OL,12,FOn the first try, the chocolate
OL,13,Fcracked and broke when chocolatiers
OL,14,Ftook it out of the mould, but on the
OL,15,Fsecond attempt, the egg was assembled
OL,16,Fin four pieces to make sure it would
OL,17,Fnot break.
