OL,3,CChocolate makers create UK's 'biggest
OL,4,Cand heaviest' Easter egg
OL,6,FGiant Easter eggs seem to be all the
OL,7,Frage at the moment, with Cadbury World
OL,8,Fcrafting the world's largest Creme Egg
OL,9,Fwhich weighs 45kg and is 3ft tall.
OL,11,FCocoba is no stranger to dabbling in
OL,12,Fgiant eggs, with its 2kg and 4kg
OL,13,FEaster eggs being bestsellers.
OL,15,FThe latest 300kg egg was born out of a
OL,16,Fproduct review last year which
OL,17,Fchallenged the chocolate brand to go
OL,18,Fheavier for 2025.
