OL,3,CChocolate makers create UK's 'biggest
OL,4,Cand heaviest' Easter egg
OL,6,FWhen Cocoba founder Darren Litton saw
OL,7,Fthe review, he joked the chocolatiers
OL,8,Fneeded to set their sights on a bigger
OL,9,Fcreation.
OL,11,FMr Litton said: "We don't take
OL,12,Fourselves too seriously and as the
OL,13,Fexperts in creating giant chocolate
OL,14,Feggs, we all had great fun in bringing
OL,15,Fthis 300kg mega egg to life.
