OL,3,CChocolate makers create UK's 'biggest
OL,4,Cand heaviest' Easter egg
OL,6,F"We are also passionate about making
OL,7,Fpremium chocolate products with a
OL,8,Fdifference, and it's nice to be able
OL,9,Fto give something back to community by
OL,10,Fdonating some of our profits.
OL,11,FParticularly as we are aware of
OL,12,Fongoing cost-of-living challenges and
OL,13,Fthe rising price of chocolate."
OL,15,FLukasz Zajac, head chocolate engineer,
OL,16,Fsaid making the egg was "quite
OL,17,Ftechnical" because of factors
OL,18,Fincluding chocolate shrinking when it
OL,19,Fcools down.
